\begin_layout Subsection
Margins
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Every page of the dissertation or thesis must have a one inch margin on
 all sides (top, bottom, left and right).
 However, the page number may appear outside of these margins.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Please Note: These minimum specifications also apply to all figures, charts,
 graphs, illustrations and appendices.
\end_layout

